<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-warm-gray">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-forest rounded-sm overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
          <img
            src="/broker-photo.jpg"
            alt="Your Palm Beach Broker"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            onerror="this.style.background='#2D5016'; this.style.display='flex';"
          />
        </div>
        <!-- Gold accent border -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-full h-full border-2 border-gold rounded-sm -z-10"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div>
        <p class="font-sans text-gold tracking-widest uppercase text-sm mb-3">Meet Your Broker</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl lg:text-5xl text-forest font-light leading-tight mb-6">
          Your Palm Beach<br />
          <span class="text-gold">Broker</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="w-16 h-px bg-gold mb-8"></div>

        <div class="space-y-5 font-sans text-warm-gray-dark leading-relaxed text-base">
          <p>I was born and raised in Cuba, where I completed my studies and graduated as an Accounting Technician. From an early age, I developed a strong passion for numbers, structure, and organization, along with a deep desire to help others.</p>
          <p>At the age of 20, I emigrated to the United States and began a decade long career in the medical field. Through dedication and perseverance, I advanced professionally and had the opportunity to work alongside one of the most prestigious surgeons in Palm Beach County. While the experience was incredibly rewarding, my entrepreneurial mindset was always present, pushing me to pursue a career where I could build, lead, and create long term impact.</p>
          <p>That journey led me to real estate — a field where strategy, numbers, negotiation, and people all come together. Becoming a real estate professional has been a true blessing, allowing me to help buyers and sellers navigate one of the most important financial and personal decisions of their lives. My approach is client centered, results driven, and built on trust. My goal is always to exceed expectations and ensure every transaction reaches a successful closing.</p>
          <p>I am known as a strong, committed leader who advocates relentlessly for my clients. Their goals are my priority, and I treat every transaction with the same level of care, urgency, and attention to detail as if it were my own.</p>
          <p>Outside of real estate, I value an active and balanced lifestyle. I enjoy running, working out, and golfing. I am also a proud mother of two beautiful children, which has deepened my understanding of the importance of home, stability, and community. This personal perspective fuels my passion for helping clients not just buy or sell property — but find a place they can truly call home.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/#contact" class="inline-block bg-gold text-white font-sans text-xs tracking-widest uppercase py-4 px-8 hover:bg-gold/90 transition-all duration-300">
            Work With Me
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/yourpalmbeachbroker/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-forest text-forest font-sans text-xs tracking-widest uppercase py-4 px-8 hover:bg-forest hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zM12 0C8.741 0 8.333.014 7.053.072 2.695.272.273 2.69.073 7.052.014 8.333 0 8.741 0 12c0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98C8.333 23.986 8.741 24 12 24c3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98C15.668.014 15.259 0 12 0zm0 5.838a6.162 6.162 0 100 12.324 6.162 6.162 0 000-12.324zM12 16a4 4 0 110-8 4 4 0 010 8zm6.406-11.845a1.44 1.44 0 100 2.881 1.44 1.44 0 000-2.881z"/></svg>
            Instagram
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
